Who Is Zoe Duchesne? Biography & Parents

Zoe Duchesne is an actress, model, and social media personality. Zoe Duchesne is known for the TV projects such as Evian (2005), Comadisco (2005), She's a Superstar (2007), and Les Ex (2017).

Zoe Duchesne has become one of the trending topics on the internet. Many people are searching for her biography details and personal life. However, Zoe Duchesne doesn't have an official Wikipedia page.

The actress was raised by her parents in Montreal, Canada. The identity of her parents is unknown in the media. Zoe loves to keep her personal life a secret and avoid the media's eyes. However, she has shared her picture with her parents and showcased them on her social media account.

On 21 June 2020, Zoe uploads her picture with her dad on the occasion of Father's Day via an Instagram post. Furthermore, she grew up with her siblings, but their names and identity are unknown at the moment.

Zoe Duchesne was born on 15 December 1986 in Canada. She is 36 years of age and has a zodiac sign of Sagittarius. Furthermore, the 36-year-old actress holds a Canadian nationality and belongs to the white ethnicity. In addition, she follows the Christianity religion.

Her approximate height is around 5 feet 8 inches or 1.72 m tall, and she has a decent weight of about 52 kg or 114 lbs. There is no information available about her educational background.

Zoe Duchesne's Married Life

Many people are curious whether Zoe Duchesne is married or not. Well, the Canadian actress is not married yet. However, she is dating her boyfriend named Guillaume Salmon 2017. Her boyfriend, Guillaume Salmon is an entrepreneur by profession.

Zoe Duchesne frequently uploads her picture with her boyfriend and showcased them on her social media. On 13 December 2020, Zoe uploads her picture with her beau and celebrated their three years together as a couple.

Her boyfriend, Guillaume Salmon is available on Instagram with the username @_guillaumesalmon_ and he has more than 20.4k followers on his Instagram page. The couple hasn't mentioned about to get married yet.

Net Worth & Career

Zoe Duchesne has an estimated net worth of about $500 thousand. She earned this fortune from her professional career as an actress and model. Zoe Duchesne is active in the showbiz industry since 2003 and has been credited with 13 TV appearances as an actress.

Due to her experience and acting skills, Zoe Duchesne has been able to earn a decent salary from her job. Besides this, she also makes money from endorsements, sponsorship deals, and paid partnerships.

Zoe Duchesne was passionate about acting and modelling since her childhood days. Likewise, she also did her modelling class during her early days. Initially, Zoe Duchesne began her career as a fashion model and she showcased her talents in various modelling shows and events.

Later. Zoe Duchesne made her acting debut in the short film, Chanel Aqualumiere as a model in 2003. Likewise, she made her appearance in another short film, Comadisco as Girl 1 in 2005. Her breakthrough role came in 2005 when she made her appearance in the short film, Evian, directed by Meta Akkus.

Some of her notable works are La Muette (2006), Calvin Klein: Obsession (2006), Archive Again (2008), Bir Bilsen Gece Yolculari (2010), Jukebox Motel (2012), La derniere viree (2014), In America (2014-2015), and others.
